# Avermate Project Overview

This is a monorepo project using a Next.js frontend and Hono API backend.

## Repository Structure
- `apps/client/` - Next.js frontend application
- `apps/api/` - Hono API backend with Drizzle ORM and Turso/LibSQL database
- `.github/workflows/` - GitHub Actions workflows
- `patches/` - Patch files for dependencies

## Key Technologies
- Frontend: Next.js 15, React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, shadcn/ui components
- Backend: Bun, Hono, Drizzle ORM, LibSQL/Turso, Redis
- Authentication: better-auth
- State Management: React Query, nanostores
- Data Validation: Zod
- Package Manager: Bun

## Development Commands
```bash
# Start Redis (required for API)
sudo service redis-server start  # Run this in WSL

# Start the frontend development server
cd apps/client && bun dev

# Start the API development server
cd apps/api && bun dev

# Database commands
cd apps/api && bun db:studio # Open Drizzle Studio
cd apps/api && bun db:push # Push schema changes to database
cd apps/api && bun db:dev # Start local Turso development database

# Install dependencies
bun install
```


